  m_Name: DAY 4 WINDOW DRESSING LIN A
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  lines:
  - NewSpeakerName: 2
    dialogue: "Lin\u2019s Pizza! The taste that will always make you want more! What
      can I get you?"
  - NewSpeakerName: 6
    dialogue: "Uh, it\u2019s Bob. Do you know if Mrs. Perkins is missing one of her
      cats? I think I found one in my backyard."
  - NewSpeakerName: 2
    dialogue: "A cat? Well Mrs. Perkins is always losing hers\u2026 and they sometimes
      get into my leftover ingredients\u2026 But why would you call me and not her?"
  - NewSpeakerName: 6
    dialogue: "I didn\u2019t mean to\u2026 I think the switchboard operator mixed
      it up."
  - NewSpeakerName: 2
    dialogue: "Huh\u2026 well she lives close by, I\u2019ll head over and ask her.
      She\u2019ll stop by soon if that is her cat"
  - NewSpeakerName: 6
    dialogue: Works for me. Thanks, Lin!
